<h3><span class="time">8:00 - 9:00</span> 3C: Daemon Queue & Settled Batches</h3>

<div class="action">Scroll down to the "Daemon Queue" — showing pending transactions.</div>

<div class="script">
This is the Daemon Queue — the processing pipeline. Each entry shows the amount, transaction type (Shield or Public), and current status. The Daemon runs every 5 seconds, automatically picking up PENDING transactions and processing them.
<br><br>
For Shield transactions, the Daemon: generates a ZK proof, deposits into ShieldVault, then executes the shielded payout. For Public transactions, it sends directly through MultisendV2.
</div>

<div class="action">Scroll down to "Settled Batches & History" — showing completed transactions.</div>

<div class="script">
