<br>
CREATED — MATCHED — ESCROW LOCKED — EXECUTING — COMPLETED — SETTLED.
<br><br>
Each escrow has a countdown deadline. If the agent doesn't finish in time, the client gets an automatic refund. The platform fee is just 5% — the lowest in the market. And if there's a dispute, the Arbitration system handles it.
</div>

